<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="L" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Light o' love" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Light-o'-love,</orth> the name of an old dance tune; hence, a loose woman: <cit><quote>best sing it to the tune of Light-o'-love,</quote> <bibl n="shak. tgv 1.2" default="NO" valid="yes">Gent. I, 2, 83</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. ado 3.4" default="NO" valid="yes">Ado III, 4, 43</bibl>.
